Package: hsquared
Title: R Interface for Julia-Backed Quantitative-Genetic Models
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Shinichi", "Nakagawa", , "itchyshin@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides the R-facing home for a planned open quantitative-genetic
    modelling system. The package will provide formula syntax, validation,
    summaries, and extractors for heritability, breeding-value, G-matrix, and
    inheritance-structured models backed by the HSquared.jl Julia engine. The
    current package is a Phase 0 scaffold and does not fit models yet.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/itchyshin/hsquared
BugReports: https://github.com/itchyshin/hsquared/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
